OL,3,C'I was a highly functioning binge
OL,4,Cdrinker', says Ulrika Jonsson
OL,6,FUlrika Jonsson has revealed she is
OL,7,Ffour months sober after admitting she
OL,8,Fwas using alcohol to "escape from my
OL,9,Fwoes".
OL,11,FThe TV presenter told the Sun
OL,12,Fnewspaper she "sobbed like a child"
OL,13,Fafter her best friend told her she
OL,14,Fneeded help with her drinking.
OL,16,FHaving split with husband Brian Monet
OL,17,Fin 2019, Jonsson said she had "no one
OL,18,Fto lean on" amid "family problems and
OL,19,Fpersonal issues".
