OL,3,C'I was a highly functioning binge
OL,4,Cdrinker', says Ulrika Jonsson
OL,6,F"It was just me and my friend, the
OL,7,Fdrink," she told the newspaper.
OL,9,FJonsson said she knew there was a
OL,10,Fproblem because "I no longer
OL,11,Frecognised myself".
OL,13,FThe 57-year-old said she was not a
OL,14,Fregular drinker but she was heading
OL,15,Ftowards drinking every day "when
OL,16,Fthings got bad over the past year".
OL,18,F"I established a routine of drinking
OL,19,Fthen punishing myself with hard work
OL,20,Fthrough my hangover," she said.
