OL,3,C'I was a highly functioning binge
OL,4,Cdrinker', says Ulrika Jonsson
OL,6,F"And then reward myself with another
OL,7,Fdrink at the end of it all."
OL,9,FJonsson said sobriety had brought her
OL,10,F"much-needed peace".
OL,12,F"Drink quelled my anxiety," she said.
OL,14,F"I was a highly functioning binge
OL,15,Fdrinker. I never woke up dishevelled
OL,16,Fin a pool of sick.
OL,18,F"But the number of times I would black
OL,19,Fout and not recall the night before
OL,20,Fwhen I had been drinking alone, were
OL,21,Fincreasing."
