OL,3,C'I was a highly functioning binge
OL,4,Cdrinker', says Ulrika Jonsson
OL,6,FJonsson said that drinking "stifled my
OL,7,Fanger" as she used it to "remember the
OL,8,Fgood times and to forget the present
OL,9,Fbad times".
OL,11,F"It was the perfect escape from my
OL,12,Fwoes," she told the newspaper.
OL,14,F"When I drank, I felt I became a
OL,15,Fbetter, nicer person, and more
OL,16,Fequipped to cope.
OL,18,F"The truth, of course, was quite the
OL,19,Fopposite."
